00:20:22,040 --> 00:20:24,119
- Why are you so stingy?
- Hey. Look.

259
00:20:24,120 --> 00:20:25,520
- What?
- Look there.

260
00:20:37,600 --> 00:20:39,320
Hey, is your girlfriend there?

261
00:20:43,600 --> 00:20:45,280
I'm alone down here.

262
00:20:46,080 --> 00:20:48,920
Hey, you said you'd introduce me
to the love of your life.

263
00:20:49,720 --> 00:20:51,320
- Right.
- Where is she?

264
00:20:52,360 --> 00:20:53,480
She'll be here.

265
00:20:57,600 --> 00:20:59,280
Peace be upon you.

266
00:21:01,520 --> 00:21:02,999
Peace be upon you too.

267
00:21:03,000 --> 00:21:04,400
Hey.

268
00:21:05,000 --> 00:21:06,000
The love of my life.

269
00:21:09,760 --> 00:21:11,479
Husniya Radwa,

270
00:21:11,480 --> 00:21:13,160
my future fiancée.

271
00:21:14,080 --> 00:21:17,160
Hey! When did I become
your future fiancée?

272
00:21:18,560 --> 00:21:20,720
When you agree later.

273
00:21:23,320 --> 00:21:24,559
Let me introduce him to you.

274
00:21:24,560 --> 00:21:26,720
This is my friend, Farez.

275
00:21:28,280 --> 00:21:29,360
Hi, Farez.

276
00:21:49,000 --> 00:21:51,000
Fiancée?

277
00:21:53,200 --> 00:21:54,200
Fiancée?

278
00:21:56,160 --> 00:21:57,399
Husniya is mine.

279
00:21:57,400 --> 00:21:59,520
Husniya is really mine.

280
00:22:00,040 --> 00:22:02,679
Husniya is mine!

281
00:22:02,680 --> 00:22:05,440
Mine!

282
00:22:07,520 --> 00:22:09,160
Husniya is mine!

283
00:22:16,120 --> 00:22:17,680
We've known each other.

284
00:22:19,480 --> 00:22:20,560
We've met.

285
00:22:23,120 --> 00:22:24,760
I'm sorry, Husniya.

286
00:22:26,760 --> 00:22:29,360
Your future fiancé, Thariq Ridzuwan,

287
00:22:30,760 --> 00:22:31,720
is dead.

288
00:22:35,000 --> 00:22:36,280
Let's get married, honey.

289
00:24:51,360 --> 00:24:52,200
So,

290
00:24:54,040 --> 00:24:55,840
when will you agree to be my fiancée?

291
00:25:01,480 --> 00:25:02,479
Are you ready?

292
00:25:02,480 --> 00:25:04,640
I'm ready to be your husband.

293
00:25:11,280 --> 00:25:13,040
Are you sure I'm your soulmate?

294
00:25:15,520 --> 00:25:17,520
Why are you so sure?
- Because...

295
00:25:19,560 --> 00:25:23,200
"Please make Husniya Radwa my wife."

296
00:25:23,840 --> 00:25:25,880
I pray for that every day.

297
00:25:27,600 --> 00:25:29,759
Every prayer we make

298
00:25:29,760 --> 00:25:32,079
will be answered.

299
00:25:32,080 --> 00:25:35,800
Okay, we can get engaged,
but with one condition.

300
00:25:38,000 --> 00:25:38,839
I agree.

301
00:25:38,840 --> 00:25:40,399
I haven't said anything.

302
00:25:40,400 --> 00:25:42,160
Listen to me.

303
00:25:42,840 --> 00:25:46,920
I can even buy you a tank, you know?

304
00:25:47,760 --> 00:25:49,840
Why should I ask for a tank?

305
00:25:52,040 --> 00:25:54,040
Then? What's your condition?

306
00:25:55,200 --> 00:25:57,879
In the final match tomorrow,
you have to win.

307
00:25:57,880 --> 00:25:59,400
Then we can get engaged.

308
00:26:00,160 --> 00:26:01,200
What if I lose?

309
00:26:04,440 --> 00:26:06,079
If you lose,

310
00:26:06,080 --> 00:26:09,880
it means you're not sincere
in being my fiancé.

311
00:26:12,440 --> 00:26:15,759
No, listen.

312
00:26:15,760 --> 00:26:17,079
I promise you.

313
00:26:17,080 --> 00:26:18,759
In the final fight,

314
00:26:18,760 --> 00:26:19,999
I will win.

315
00:26:20,000 --> 00:26:21,360
That's my promise to you.

316
00:26:24,080 --> 00:26:25,920
- Promise?
- I promise.

317
00:26:27,360 --> 00:26:30,119
I promise. Easy fight.

318
00:26:30,120 --> 00:26:31,799
Okay, we'll see.

319
00:26:31,800 --> 00:26:32,999
- Okay, let's go.
- You'll get it if you lose.

320
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:36,720
- Okay, but what if I win?
- I'll be your fiancée.

321
00:26:53,640 --> 00:26:55,400
Did I do anything wrong?

322
00:27:00,840 --> 00:27:02,040
Why are you upset with me?

323
00:27:04,120 --> 00:27:05,280
I was

324
00:27:07,560 --> 00:27:10,520
bullied from my first year
to my last year of school, Ridz.

325
00:27:13,400 --> 00:27:15,080
They called me stupid,

326
00:27:16,800 --> 00:27:17,800
soft,

327
00:27:19,400 --> 00:27:20,440
and a sissy.

328
00:27:22,400 --> 00:27:24,280
When they were tired of calling me names,

329
00:27:25,360 --> 00:27:26,840
they'd prank me.

330
00:27:28,440 --> 00:27:30,280
They threw my shoes in the toilet.

331
00:27:31,920 --> 00:27:35,480
They spat on my food and cut my hair.

332
00:27:37,720 --> 00:27:40,679
They stripped me off in front of everyone.

333
00:27:40,680 --> 00:27:42,120
You report to the teachers?

334
00:27:43,280 --> 00:27:44,120
I did.

335
00:27:46,080 --> 00:27:49,000
I was beaten up every day
because of that, Ridz.

336
00:27:51,040 --> 00:27:51,880
Your dad?

337
00:27:53,880 --> 00:27:54,840
I told him,

338
00:27:56,680 --> 00:27:58,360
but he'd beat me up too.

339
00:28:01,000 --> 00:28:02,120
He was embarrassed.

340
00:28:03,280 --> 00:28:04,840
To have a sissy son like me.

341
00:28:07,800 --> 00:28:09,640
He was the one who called me sissy.

342
00:28:12,040 --> 00:28:13,640
For my entire life, Ridz,

343
00:28:15,120 --> 00:28:16,360
I was a loser.

344
00:28:18,280 --> 00:28:20,280
I've never won anything.

345
00:28:20,880 --> 00:28:22,360
I've never achieved anything.

346
00:28:23,960 --> 00:28:26,560
But for the first time in my life,

347
00:28:28,040 --> 00:28:29,160
I know what I want.

348
00:28:32,040 --> 00:28:33,280
I want...

349
00:28:34,400 --> 00:28:35,800
I really want

350
00:28:37,520 --> 00:28:39,120
to win the tournament tomorrow.

351
00:28:42,600 --> 00:28:44,080
We're friends, right?

352
00:28:46,800 --> 00:28:48,120
I'm your brother, right?

353
00:28:49,440 --> 00:28:51,120
I hope you can help me, Ridz.

354
00:28:58,240 --> 00:28:59,519
You want me to withdraw?

355
00:28:59,520 --> 00:29:01,320
No, don't.

356
00:29:02,160 --> 00:29:03,520
I want us to fight,

357
00:29:04,880 --> 00:29:06,120
but I want to win.

358
00:29:07,040 --> 00:29:08,120
Can I?

359
00:29:10,200 --> 00:29:11,440
Ridz, if you

360
00:29:12,960 --> 00:29:14,800
really take me as your brother,

361
00:29:16,320 --> 00:29:18,480
I hope you'll let me win tomorrow.

362
00:29:21,840 --> 00:29:23,040
Please.

363
00:29:33,360 --> 00:29:37,400
Let's invite
our special juror, Mr. Adrean.

364
00:29:44,760 --> 00:29:47,400
The first finalist is Farez!

365
00:29:54,480 --> 00:29:57,520
His opponent will be Thariq Ridzuwan!

366
00:29:59,600 --> 00:30:00,720
Thariq!

367
00:30:09,240 --> 00:30:11,640
Boys, let's have a clean fight.

368
00:30:12,840 --> 00:30:14,559
The rules are easy.

369
00:30:14,560 --> 00:30:16,200
Do not hit the back of his head.

370
00:30:17,080 --> 00:30:18,440
Do not hit his neck

371
00:30:19,040 --> 00:30:20,559
and his groin.

372
00:30:20,560 --> 00:30:21,640
And no elbow.

373
00:30:22,960 --> 00:30:24,400
Always protect yourselves, boys.

374
00:30:25,920 --> 00:30:26,760
Touch gloves.

375
00:30:28,040 --> 00:30:29,520
Friends forever?

376
00:30:34,920 --> 00:30:35,800
Ready?

377
00:30:37,680 --> 00:30:38,520
Fight.

378
00:30:52,080 --> 00:30:53,439
Ridz, are you okay?

379
00:30:53,440 --> 00:30:55,679
- I'm okay.
- Ridz.

380
00:30:55,680 --> 00:30:57,759
- Just stop this fight, please.
- Hey.

381
00:30:57,760 --> 00:30:59,680
- I'm okay.
- Ridz.

382
00:31:00,240 --> 00:31:01,560
- Can you continue?
- Yes, I can.

383
00:31:03,720 --> 00:31:05,440
You promised to win, right?

384
00:31:06,480 --> 00:31:07,599
Yes.

385
00:31:07,600 --> 00:31:09,999
How are you going to win
if you don't fight properly?

386
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:11,280
Okay, okay.

387
00:31:19,240 --> 00:31:20,920
- Ready?
- Ready.

388
00:31:23,560 --> 00:31:24,400
Fight.

389
00:31:35,280 --> 00:31:37,359
Stop. Stop!

390
00:31:37,360 --> 00:31:39,879
Farez!

391
00:31:39,880 --> 00:31:41,359
Last warning.

392
00:31:41,360 --> 00:31:43,160
No elbow.

393
00:31:46,840 --> 00:31:48,279
Good, my friend.

394
00:31:48,280 --> 00:31:50,639
Let Husniya see that you're a softy.

395
00:31:50,640 --> 00:31:52,440
Like a sissy boy.

396
00:31:58,320 --> 00:31:59,240
Ready?

397
00:32:01,920 --> 00:32:02,760
Fight.

398
00:32:32,360 --> 00:32:33,599
Stop.

399
00:32:33,600 --> 00:32:35,560
Ridz, stop.

400
00:32:43,720 --> 00:32:46,720
- I'll stop this fight.
- No, I'm okay.

401
00:32:48,160 --> 00:32:50,920
I can still fight.
Please don't stop this fight.

402
00:32:51,720 --> 00:32:52,600
I will win.

403
00:32:56,240 --> 00:32:57,080
Ridz.

404
00:32:58,120 --> 00:33:01,120
Farez's ribs could be cracked,
if not broken.

405
00:33:07,400 --> 00:33:10,039
Farez. Hey, stop.

406
00:33:10,040 --> 00:33:12,239
Stop, stop, stop.

407
00:33:12,240 --> 00:33:14,639
You don't want me to win, do you?

408
00:33:14,640 --> 00:33:16,560
Because you promised Husniya you'd win.

409
00:33:18,280 --> 00:33:20,000
I won't let you marry her, Ridz.

410
00:33:21,320 --> 00:33:22,440
You stole her from me.

411
00:33:23,360 --> 00:33:24,760
You betrayed me, Ridz.

412
00:33:27,360 --> 00:33:30,680
The girl who saved your life...

413
00:33:32,400 --> 00:33:33,520
is Radwa?

414
00:33:38,840 --> 00:33:43,520
Farez, please. Please stop. Enough.

415
00:33:45,440 --> 00:33:47,400
You took her away from me, Ridz.

416
00:33:49,560 --> 00:33:51,159
Farez, she doesn't even know you.

417
00:33:51,160 --> 00:33:53,240
You haven't even met her.
What are you talking about?

418
00:33:54,120 --> 00:33:57,800
In my whole life,
I want nothing but Husniya.

419
00:33:58,640 --> 00:34:02,399
I'm alive now
and I want to keep living for her.

420
00:34:02,400 --> 00:34:03,359
I love her, Ridz.

421
00:34:03,360 --> 00:34:04,879
Farez, enough.

422
00:34:04,880 --> 00:34:06,999
- I love her, Ridz.
- Farez.

423
00:34:07,000 --> 00:34:09,638
Whether you win or lose,
she'll never choose you.

424
00:34:09,639 --> 00:34:11,320
It's enough.

425
00:34:12,040 --> 00:34:14,080
- Stop it.
- I don't just want to win!

426
00:34:14,600 --> 00:34:16,159
I want you to die.

427
00:34:53,880 --> 00:34:55,678
What are you doing?

428
00:34:55,679 --> 00:34:57,440
I called Husniya, Ridz.

429
00:35:00,200 --> 00:35:04,200
I told her that she was the reason
I didn't commit suicide.

430
00:35:05,840 --> 00:35:09,880
She saved me, so I want to save her.

431
00:35:10,600 --> 00:35:11,680
You know what she said?

432
00:35:13,720 --> 00:35:17,200
She said you can save her, Ridz.

433
00:35:20,160 --> 00:35:21,760
You will take care of her.

434
00:35:29,800 --> 00:35:31,879
- What are you doing?
- Husniya is mine, Ridz.

435
00:35:31,880 --> 00:35:33,359
- Farez!
- Ridz!

436
00:35:33,360 --> 00:35:35,719
- Husniya is mine.
- Are you crazy?

437
00:35:35,720 --> 00:35:38,319
Husniya is mine. Let me go.

438
00:35:38,320 --> 00:35:39,240
Come with me.

439
00:35:40,120 --> 00:35:41,520
Get out now.

440
00:35:42,640 --> 00:35:44,760
- I will kill you, Ridz.
- Get out.

441
00:36:00,680 --> 00:36:01,759
What happened to Farez?

442
00:36:01,760 --> 00:36:03,359
He was dismissed.

443
00:36:03,360 --> 00:36:06,280
They escorted him out.
This is for you, Ridz.

444
00:36:08,240 --> 00:36:09,320
I'll go first.

445
00:36:35,080 --> 00:36:37,080
I'M OBSESSED WITH YOUR GIRLFRIEND...

446
00:36:53,160 --> 00:36:54,800
Long time no see, my friend.

447
00:37:00,320 --> 00:37:01,160
Farez.

448
00:37:02,920 --> 00:37:04,600
Stay away from Radwa.

449
00:37:06,240 --> 00:37:07,480
I want her, Ridz.

450
00:37:08,120 --> 00:37:09,399
Why do I have to stay away?

451
00:37:09,400 --> 00:37:11,119
Because she's my future fiancée.

452
00:37:11,120 --> 00:37:13,399
She's my future wife.

453
00:37:13,400 --> 00:37:15,240
I love her way more than you do.

454
00:37:16,120 --> 00:37:19,720
Leave Husniya now
or I won't hesitate to hurt her.

455
00:37:20,320 --> 00:37:21,880
If you really love her,

456
00:37:23,200 --> 00:37:24,720
you won't hurt her.

457
00:37:25,960 --> 00:37:29,200
This is not love. This is an obsession.
Don't be a psychopath.

458
00:37:30,600 --> 00:37:34,240
Is there a difference
between love and an obsession?

459
00:37:35,600 --> 00:37:37,680
Most importantly, she's mine.

460
00:37:38,280 --> 00:37:41,439
I'd rather have her dead
than have her date you, Ridz.

461
00:37:41,440 --> 00:37:43,119
Come on, Farez.

462
00:37:43,120 --> 00:37:45,480
Radwa hasn't done anything wrong to you.

463
00:37:46,080 --> 00:37:49,480
She made the biggest mistake
when she chose you, Ridz.

464
00:37:50,040 --> 00:37:52,479
For that, she should die.

465
00:37:52,480 --> 00:37:53,880
What do you want me to do?

466
00:37:59,320 --> 00:38:00,960
As long as Radwa is safe.

467
00:38:04,360 --> 00:38:05,680
Leave her.

468
00:38:07,600 --> 00:38:09,560
Let her hate you.

469
00:38:10,760 --> 00:38:13,360
And then don't ever see her again.

470
00:38:19,640 --> 00:38:20,480
Okay.

471
00:38:22,320 --> 00:38:23,280
I'll do it.

472
00:38:27,640 --> 00:38:28,960
But you must promise me.

473
00:38:31,240 --> 00:38:33,520
Don't ever see Radwa.

474
00:38:43,360 --> 00:38:44,200
Okay.

475
00:38:45,960 --> 00:38:47,600
I won't get her.

476
00:38:49,160 --> 00:38:50,480
Neither will you.

477
00:39:05,920 --> 00:39:07,320
Honey.

478
00:39:24,720 --> 00:39:25,800
To me,

479
00:39:27,720 --> 00:39:29,600
you're dead.

480
00:39:36,120 --> 00:39:37,800
<i>I know I was wrong,</i>

481
00:39:39,360 --> 00:39:43,240
<i>but there are some things we can only love</i>

482
00:39:44,400 --> 00:39:46,160
<i>and not own.</i>

483
00:39:46,720 --> 00:39:48,680
Damn you, Farez!

484
00:39:49,560 --> 00:39:51,360
You hurt Radwa!

485
00:39:53,680 --> 00:39:56,120
It doesn't matter
if I hurt her or anything.

486
00:39:56,760 --> 00:39:59,880
The problem now is,
you broke our deal, bro.

487
00:40:00,960 --> 00:40:05,400
We agreed before.
We won't get Husniya Radwa, but you...

488
00:40:06,600 --> 00:40:09,200
- You married her, bro.
- Who are you calling stupid?

489
00:40:10,480 --> 00:40:12,480
Who broke the deal?

490
00:40:13,240 --> 00:40:15,320
Who kidnapped Radwa?

491
00:40:16,920 --> 00:40:17,760
Right?

492
00:40:18,280 --> 00:40:20,239
I planned it so well.

493
00:40:20,240 --> 00:40:22,640
I even bought a house for Husniya.

494
00:40:23,960 --> 00:40:25,920
I just needed to propose to her,

495
00:40:27,040 --> 00:40:29,160
but you came and ruined it!

496
00:40:30,800 --> 00:40:32,840
You wanted to take her away.

497
00:40:33,520 --> 00:40:35,280
And you want to kill me?

498
00:40:36,840 --> 00:40:39,759
I'm waiting for you to divorce Husniya.
Then I'll marry her.

499
00:40:39,760 --> 00:40:42,040
What the hell are you talking about?

500
00:40:44,520 --> 00:40:46,600
You impregnated her sister, bro.

501
00:40:48,520 --> 00:40:52,200
Husniya Radwa will never trust you
until she dies.

502
00:40:54,600 --> 00:40:57,800
What? You want to have a DNA test?

503
00:40:58,640 --> 00:40:59,560
No need.

504
00:41:00,720 --> 00:41:04,119
I can swear that the baby
her sister is carrying will die

505
00:41:04,120 --> 00:41:05,960
before you take a test.

506
00:41:06,600 --> 00:41:08,240
You'd kill a baby in the womb?

507
00:41:10,360 --> 00:41:12,880
Stupid? You're stupid too.

508
00:41:14,000 --> 00:41:17,120
If we want to do something bad,
we have to do it cleanly.

509
00:41:18,000 --> 00:41:20,200
Get rid of all the evidence.

510
00:41:24,840 --> 00:41:27,640
You mean you want to kill Zafir?

511
00:41:42,680 --> 00:41:43,720
Where are you going?

512
00:41:47,080 --> 00:41:48,760
The boss said thanks

513
00:41:49,680 --> 00:41:52,320
and you can go and die.

514
00:42:01,560 --> 00:42:05,520
{\an8}TO BE CONTINUED

515
00:42:13,160 --> 00:42:14,480
{\an8}From now on,

516
00:42:16,120 --> 00:42:18,120
{\an8}you'll be with me all the time.

517
00:42:18,640 --> 00:42:20,119
{\an8}Understand me?

518
00:42:20,120 --> 00:42:23,120
{\an8}It's time to execute our final plan.

519
00:42:24,280 --> 00:42:25,719
{\an8}Plan? What plan?

520
00:42:25,720 --> 00:42:29,000
{\an8}My love for you is not as strong

521
00:42:31,000 --> 00:42:32,720
{\an8}as the fear of losing you.

522
00:42:33,680 --> 00:42:35,600
{\an8}I'd rather we break up

523
00:42:38,080 --> 00:42:39,679
{\an8}than have you die.

524
00:42:39,680 --> 00:42:42,680
{\an8}You all can stop trying to make me stupid.

525
00:42:44,720 --> 00:42:46,480
{\an8}You caused problems for Thariq.

526
00:42:47,920 --> 00:42:49,559
{\an8}So you are stupid. Got that?

527
00:42:49,560 --> 00:42:51,360
{\an8}NEXT EPISODE PREVIEW

